## Key Decisions Made
- Game: 1v1 Crash PVP with crypto betting + house rake + double crash jackpot
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite (user preference)
- Backend: INSFORGE (Postgres, auth, storage, edge functions, AI gateway)
- Infra: Cloudflare (Pages/Workers for edge)
- Package manager: pnpm (not npm)
- I18n: English primary, user-selectable language
- Market: Global + Argentina/LatAm
- Legal: Agents must analyze compliance before fiat on-ramps (MercadoPago/Stripe)
- Autonomy: Full autonomous mode with human escalation for business decisions and tool access
- Multi-model: Fable for coordinator/strategy, Opus for architecture, Sonnet for execution
- Branding: Name and identity to be defined by agents in Cycle 1

